{"tid":810812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偷機車被抓怕被罰　強國男當街放尿再喝下","createTime":"2018-09-08T09:28:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T11:19:20.000Z","uid":179810,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0fd3f2e15a86812ab2a23c1774bd0691e50eaac4","tid":810812,"uid":179810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180906/1424765/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180906%2F1424765%2F&d=uQwPir3gsIxEKPjvnYVJgfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=be735c9d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180906%2F1424765%2F&h=e08a0db6\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180906/1424765/</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180906/640_1b481d2396b416d3fa04bf2051772dae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180906%2F640_1b481d2396b416d3fa04bf2051772dae.jpg&h=2f20b40e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n中國河南鄭州一名大叔，周三（5日）上午偷了一輛機車後，被人發現並報警。大叔發現走投無路，為了逃避處罰，便假裝自己有病，他從包包內拿出一個藥瓶，當街在瓶內放尿後，自己喝下。有大媽看了後，噁心到被嚇跑。目擊者稱，他喝了3瓶多。<br />\r\n <br />\r\n警方表示，周三上午11時許，大叔在花園路上偷了一輛粉紅色機車，但被民眾發現並報警。大叔於是騎著偷來的車，向西一路逃竄，但後來遭員警堵住去路。男子見走投無路，只好停下。沒想到，大叔到一顆路樹旁邊坐下後，突然取出一個小瓶，並對著瓶內放尿，然後當眾喝下，前後至少重複兩次，讓圍觀民眾目瞪口呆。<br />\r\n <br />\r\n有員警說，這名大叔叫焦新建，52歲，鄭州金水區人，是一名偷機車的慣犯，這次會喝尿，大概是想裝神經病，看能不能脫罪。不過他喝完尿後，仍被移送法辦。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"c9298a7b714d737fc9862ecab3b91498aacb1110","tid":810812,"uid":206364,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T09:37:01.000Z","msg":"加多條公眾地方行為不檢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71569e452dd9163f20ea8b2735978e13bc4a28f8","tid":810812,"uid":27396,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T10:41:16.000Z","msg":"洗唔洗飲三杯咁多。。。"},{"pid":"d9ab502856c00831e21deb30f1b7efed0d57448f","tid":810812,"uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"第一次見支那人冇周圍痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}